CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

March 19, 2014

[Cite as 03119/2014 Case Announcements, 2014-Ohio-1030.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2013-1694. State ex rel. Cincinnati Enquirer v. Hunter.

Hamilton App. No. C-130072. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hamilton County.

Upon consideration of the motion of James F. Bogen to withdraw as counsel for Judge Trade Hunter, it is ordered by the court that the motion is denied.
